///|
/// Package overview:
///
/// - `types.mbt` holds parser-facing model types and public naming helpers.
/// - `capabilities.mbt` defines capability constructors used across formats.
/// - `context.mbt` owns parse-context defaults and policy mutation helpers.
/// - `registry.mbt` is the single sync/async dispatch surface.
/// - `constructors.mbt` contains parser/result convenience builders.
